ata-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3613183\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 10, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104gaj1665702642705.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/gaj1665702642705.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/gaj1665702642705.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"gaj1665702642705\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Enable JavaScript\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Determines whether JavaScript is allowed to be executed in the widget. <code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">True</code> (default) or <code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code>.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gaj1665702642705__section_w820ab1b5b1_w821ab1b5_w822ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"gaj1665702642705__table_d12188e1_d12189e1_d12190e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"gaj1665702642705__table_d12188e1_d12189e1_d12190e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"gaj1665702642705__table_d12188e1_d12189e1_d12190e1__entry__2\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gaj1665702642705__table_d12188e1_d12189e1_d12190e1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">True</code> (default) </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gaj1665702642705__table_d12188e1_d12189e1_d12190e1__entry__2\">\n Allow JavaScript to be executed in the widget.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gaj1665702642705__table_d12188e1_d12189e1_d12190e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gaj1665702642705__table_d12188e1_d12189e1_d12190e1__entry__2\">Do not allow JavaScript to be executed in the\n                        widget. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gaj1665702642705__section_gm4_rk3_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d406383e112\">Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"gaj1665702642705__table_d12191e1_d12192e1_d12193e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Dynamic? </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> No </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Supported in Grid? </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> No </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Dependencies: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> None </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gaj1665702642705__section_dk1_5k3_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d406383e158\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gaj1665702642705__p_d103337e1_d103338e1_d103339e1\">When enabled, you can use JavaScript to call\n            extended triggers.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gaj1665702642705__section_qdx_5k3_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d406383e173\">Using in ProcScript</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gaj1665702642705__p_d108977e1_d108978e1_d108979e1\">This is a static property. It cannot be set in\n            ProcScript.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gaj1665702642705__section_oc3_wk3_wwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d406383e182\">Applies To</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ied1665702642247.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ied1665702642247.html\" title=\"The uhtml widget is a field-level widget in a form component that renders HTML code (including HTML, CSS, and JavaScript) or displays a web page (when the field value is a URL prefixed by an ampersand (&amp;www.mysite.com/doc/index.html). Uniface provides a logical widget called HTML, which is mapped to uhtml.\">uhtml (HTML Widget)</a></p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613183\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613183\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Enable JavaScript Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Enable JavaScript Determines whether JavaScript is allowed to be executed in the widget. True (default) or False . Value Description True (default) Allow JavaScript to be executed in the widget. False Do not allow JavaScript to be executed in the widget. Usage Dynamic? No Supported in Grid? No Dependencies: None Description When enabled, you can use JavaScript to call extended triggers. Using in ProcScript This is a static property. It cannot be set in ProcScript. Applies To uhtml (HTML Widget) Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}